<div class="col-md-12">
    <p>
        West Bengal Has The Widest Variety Of Attractions. Entertainment & Nightclubs – You Name It And The State Has It.
        Kolkata, The Capital Of West Bengal Has Come Of Age To Be The Cultural Capital Of India. It's Abundant In Music, Dance, And Drama & Multiplexes Are Coming Up At A Rapid Pace In West Bengal. The Fast-Growing Middle Class Population And Consumerism Over The Decade Are The Major Force In Driving Demand In The Entertainment Sector. The Tremendous Hike In The Number Of Club, Pub, Disco, In West Bengal Is The Direct Result Of Globalization.
    </p>
    <p>
        There Are Various Places Place Which Comes Live & Loud At Night With Well Known Bands Playing Music Of All Sorts And People Enjoying Drinks And Dancing Away Till Mid Night. 
    </p>
    <h4 class="text-info">Nightlife In Kolkata</h4>
    <p>
        Go To A Night Club For Partying Whole Night. Kolkata's Nightspots Are A Great Place To Unwind In.
        Nightlife In Kolkata & Darjeeling Is Tailor Made For Partygoers Who Would Like To Go Home - Or To Their Hotels - With A Tune On Their Minds.
    </p>
    <p>
        Few Popular Nightclubs And Discotheques In The City In The Town Are Listed Below
    </p>
    <h4 class="text-info">Tantra</h4>
    <p>
        Tantra Provides A Big Club Experience And Stays Open After The Other Places Close. Its Saturday Night Is The Night To Party At Tantra,
        When It Rocks Until The Sun Comes Up During The Week Tends To Be Much Quieter. Wednesdays Are Hip Hop Night.
    </p>
    <h4 class="text-info">Someplace Else</h4>
    <p>
        For A Taste Of Live Music And A Real Pub Atmosphere, The Place To Be Is Someplace Else. It Feels A Little Strange To See Indian Cover Bands Playing Western Rock Songs, But They Do It To Perfection And The Atmosphere Is Alive. 
    </p>
    <h4 class="text-info">Aqua</h4>
    <p>
        A Relatively New Addition To The Kolkata Party Scene, Aqua Is A Bar With A Difference. It's Completely Open Air With A Swimming Pool In The Middle. There's A Resident DJ, An Inviting Cocktail List, As Well As Lounges And Private Shamiana Style Tents For Chilling Out. The Music Ranges From Relaxed Progressive To Uplifting Trance. 
    </p>
    <h4 class="text-info">Underground</h4>
    <p>
        Underground Was The Preferred Venue For Kolkata's Creatures Of The Night
        Djs Spin A Mixture Of Electro And Hip Hop, And There Are Often Special Guest Appearances.
    </p>
    <h4 class="text-info">Dublin</h4>
    <p>
        If You're Looking For Some Old-World Charm, Dublin Of ITC Sonar Bangla Sheraton & Towers Is The Place To Head For. There's Something About The Irish-Pub Appeal Of Dublin But The Dance Floor Here's As Good A Place As Any To Let Down Your Hair In.
    </p>
    <h4 class="text-info">Darjeeling Has It Own Style The Nightlife And Pub Culture</h4>
    <p>
        Unlike In Big Cities; Darjeeling Does Not Have A Very Lively Night Life. However, There Are Couple Of Pubs And Bars Where The Locals Go To Have A Drink Or Two In Peace. The Western Influence Can Be Clearly Seen Especially With Regard To Music.
        Western Country Music, Rock And Roll Defines The Very Base Of Groovy <b>Nightlife In Darjeeling</b>.
    </p>
    <h4 class="text-info">Joey's Pub</h4>
    <p>
        Joey's Pub Is Face Of Darjeeling's Nightlife. You Would Not Want To Be Missing Out On The Charm Of This Old British Style Country Pub. You Relish A Beer Or A Drink In The Company Of Nice And Warm People.
    </p>
    <h4 class="text-info">The Buzz</h4>
    <p>
        Buzz Is A Contemporary Style Pub In Darjeeling. The Decor Of This Pub Is Lovely. There Are Western Musical Instruments Showcased Inside Glass Cabins.  
    </p>
